name: Fairy lights
description: You should be very patient if you really want to see a fairy. Wake up before dawn and leave your house as quietly as you can. Don't wear shoes! It's important. Yes, I know that it's cold. Hide behind the largest, tallest tree you can find. Don't make a sound and be very very still. Wait for the first rays of sunshine. Then, if you're lucky, you might get a glimpse of fairies flying over tall grass.
